WEBVTT

00:02.612 --> 00:03.770
Your nurse is here.

00:03.820 --> 00:04.839
Your wrist, please.

00:04.846 --> 00:07.605
Are you always so impertinent?
I'm simply doing my job.

00:07.814 --> 00:09.293
I didn't catch your name.

00:09.295 --> 00:10.853
Adams.

00:10.855 --> 00:11.975
Sister Adams.

00:12.575 --> 00:14.975
This isn't a situation
I expected to find myself in.

00:16.055 --> 00:17.733
He doesn't need it.

00:17.735 --> 00:19.895
I'm not a bloody child.

00:24.295 --> 00:25.453
James.

00:25.455 --> 00:26.775
James! No!

00:32.015 --> 00:35.333
Did you tell her why you did this?

00:35.335 --> 00:37.813
No-one else is to know about this.

00:37.815 --> 00:38.975
No-one.

00:39.215 --> 00:41.453
On the boat.
Forget the boat.

00:41.455 --> 00:43.215
I thought you'd wished
you'd never married me.

00:44.335 --> 00:45.893
I missed you.

00:45.895 --> 00:47.255
I missed you too.

00:50.615 --> 00:52.413
I was glad
to receive your letter.

00:52.415 --> 00:54.413
The hospital will be lucky
to have you.

00:54.415 --> 00:55.773
If they want me, that is.

00:55.775 --> 00:58.493
I don't want him
employing the Adams woman.

00:58.495 --> 01:00.053
She said she'd be discreet.

01:00.055 --> 01:03.093
Well, she contacted George
because she has no other options.

01:03.095 --> 01:05.013
She will scuttle off
as soon as possible,

01:05.015 --> 01:08.293
and you'll just have to train
someone all over again.

01:08.295 --> 01:10.173
The job's yours if you want it.

01:10.175 --> 01:12.893
I thought I made my wishes clear.

01:12.895 --> 01:14.613
No, you misrepresented her.

01:14.639 --> 01:17.597
The fact that I want it
should suffice.

01:17.909 --> 01:19.147
Not this time.

01:19.149 --> 01:22.987
I would like to pay
your return passage to England.

01:22.989 --> 01:24.187
Did you speak to Dr Duncan?

01:24.189 --> 01:25.827
Did you encourage him against me?

01:25.829 --> 01:27.187
That is a very generous offer.

01:27.189 --> 01:28.827
You would be a fool not to accept.

01:28.829 --> 01:30.469
And you'd be a fool
to think I would.

